#Centre Window
"qdbus org.kde.kglobalaccel /component/kwin org.kde.kglobalaccel.Component.invokeShortcut 'Window Move' ; qdbus org.kde.kglobalaccel /component/kwin org.kde.kglobalaccel.Component.invokeShortcut 'MoveMouseToCenter' ; xdotool click 1"
    m:0x50 + c:84
    Mod2+Mod4 + KP_Begin

